ColorPresenter in cli/output/color.go. Carries a Theme field selecting the active theme. Every method renders from Result data using theme element lookups (e.g. t.MarkerID.Apply(idString)) instead of hardcoded color helpers. The guardrail property is maintained because Style.Apply only wraps text in ANSI codes. colorizePatch applies per-line theme coloring (DiffAdd/DiffRemove/DiffHunk) to unified diff output. The Todo method formats closures: each closure shows hash, member counts, Events section (NODE-CHANGED/NODE-ADDED/NODE-REMOVED/EDGE-ADDED/EDGE-REMOVED/BROKEN-EDGE), Members section, and Inspect/Resolve commands using the closure hash. See <ref spec="output.color_mode">color mode</ref> and <ref spec="output.theme_system">theme system</ref>.